OL,5, A British-Israeli man has told BBC     
OL,6, London of his "sheer happiness" at     
OL,7, hugging his mother after she was       
OL,8, released by Hamas.                     
OL,10,FAda Sagi, who turned 75 when being held
OL,11,Fcaptive, was freed on 28 November, the 
OL,12,Ffifth day of the Israel-Hamas truce.   
OL,14,FHer son Noam Sagi, who lives in north  
OL,15,FLondon, said: "For 53 days I was       
OL,16,Fvisualising that moment. Everything    
OL,17,Fcame into it.                          
OL,19,F"It was just squeezing and squeezing   
OL,20,Fand squeezing and pinching myself."    
